## 1. What Wave 2 gets right (preserve these — do not rebuild)

Before any objection, this needs saying plainly: the discipline in this plan is rare. Most retail quant projects never get within a mile of this rigor. The following are correct and should survive every revision.

| Decision | Verdict | Why it's right |
|---|---|---|
| GBM (LightGBM) over deep nets | **Keep** | Tabular financial data favors gradient-boosted trees; LSTMs/Transformers are marginal-at-best and overfit-prone. The research behind this is sound. |
